review.description: The market keeps getting bigger and better every year.  There are now a couple produce stands, a kettle korn place, several places selling plants an herbs, goats, bunnys, jams, breads, eggs, pork, crafts, and really nice soaps.  It is now a market worth going to if you are close by and don't want to make the trip to one of the bigger ones.
review.author: William O.
